  "title": "Purchaser/Project Administrator | From $2600 | 5 days, Office hours",
  "description": "<p><em>Join us as a Purchaser cum Project Administrator, where you’ll manage procurement of construction materials, coordinate with suppliers and project teams, and keep project documentation, purchasing, and administrative processes running smoothly. This role is ideal for someone detail-oriented, organised, and proactive, who can handle both purchasing and project support in a fast-paced construction environment.</em></p><h3>What You’ll Be Doing</h3><ul><li><p>Handle procurement and purchasing of construction materials.</p></li><li><p>Prepare purchase orders, track costs, and manage suppliers.</p></li><li><p>Coordinate with project teams, vendors, and subcontractors.</p></li><li><p>Manage project documents, contracts, and reports.</p></li><li><p>Assist with invoicing, payment tracking, and basic admin duties.</p></li><li><p>Support project coordination and progress tracking.</p></li></ul><h3>Who We’re Looking For</h3><ul><li><p>Diploma holder with <strong>min. 2 years’ construction industry experience</strong>.</p></li><li><p>Experience in procurement and project administration.</p></li><li><p>Proficient in Microsoft Office.</p></li><li><p>Well-organised, detail-oriented, and able to work independently.</p></li></ul><h3>Salary & other information</h3><ul><li><p>From $2600 - $3900 (based on experience)</p></li><li><p>5 days work week, office hours</p></li></ul><p><br />Hey Rocket Pte. Ltd. (EA 21C0816)<br />Angel Chia (R25126511)</p>",
